speaker: Unknown
text: Hey, Peter. How are you feeling today?

speaker: Unknown
text: Not great, honestly. I've had a terrible headache since this morning.

speaker: Unknown
text: Oh, no. Did you take anything for it?

speaker: Unknown
text: Yeah. I took four hundred milligrams of Advil around ten AM.

speaker: Unknown
text: Just some toast and coffee. Nothing heavy.

speaker: Unknown
text: That might explain why it's not helping as much. You probably need more food in your system.

speaker: Unknown
text: I also haven't been drinking enough water today.

speaker: Unknown
text: Dehydration could definitely make the headache worse.

speaker: Unknown
text: Try to get some rest too.
